casebody.data:
No. 578,

Misc.

Townsend v. Ogilvie, Sheriff, et al. Petitioner pro se. Daniel P. Ward and Edward J. Hladis for respondents.

Motion of George N. Leighton to withdraw his appearance as counsel for petitioner granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit denied.
